headline.main: New Owners of Houston Home Find Human Remains in Attic Wall
headline.print_headline: New Owners of Houston Home Find Human Remains in Attic Wall

lead_paragraph: The new owners of a Houston bungalow found human remains in an attic wall that may be those of the previous owner, who was declared missing two years ago.
